data.description: This adorable one story home has served one family since day one.  With growing children, they have simply outgrown it and need more space.  The home was taken care of with much care and love.  The family removed all carpet and installed wood floors in all rooms except wet areas.  Kitchen and bathrooms have tile floors.  The home has 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and a study with an open floor plan.  Perfect little home for entertaining.  The exterior has a stucco front, sprinkler system and spacious backyard.  Located minutes from I-35 for an easy commute to San Antonio or Austin.  Plenty of local restaurants and shopping close by.
